QUESTION NO: 1
Which three of the following service components are included in the design phase? (Choose
three.)
A. Account Qualification and Planning
B. Detailed Design Customer Sign-Off C. Staff Training
D. Systems Acceptance Test Plan Development
E. Proposal Development
F. Staging Plan Development
Answer: B
QUESTION NO: 2
Which of the following is an activity of the site readiness assessment service component in the
plan phase?
A. Align Business Requirements to Technical Requirements
B. Create a Plan to Recycle Used Equipment
C. Assess Infrastructure Requirements
D. Install and Test System Components in a Nonproduction Environment
Answer: C
QUESTION NO: 3
Which service component in the security implement phase includes activities such as executing
test cases, capturing test results, and tuning test procedures?
A. As-Built Documentation
B. Acceptance Testing
C. Staging
D. Define Technical Procedures
E. Network Ready for Use
Answer: B
